{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-714-Whats-New-in-Apple-Pay-and-Wallet","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC17","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","title":"What’s New in Apple Pay & Wallet"},"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Whats-new-with-Wallet","text":"What’s new with Wallet","level":2},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"mass deletion interface for your passes"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"lighter color scheme","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"from iOS 11, only encrypted NFC passes are supported. Register yours at "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/apple-pay\/","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Opt-out-of-sharing","text":"Opt-out of sharing","level":3},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Passes can now be opted-out of sharing","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Useful for single-use items, like loyalty cards or tickets"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To take advantage of this, set the new top-level ","type":"text"},{"code":"sharingProhibited","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key with value ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in your ","type":"text"},{"code":"pass.json","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing","code":["{","  ...","  \"sharingProhibited\": true,","  ...","}"]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Users can still share the pass in older versions of iOS."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Written-By","text":"Written By","level":2},{"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"zntfdr","type":"image"}]}],"size":1},{"content":[{"text":"zntfdr","anchor":"zntfdr","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr","overridingTitle":"Contributed Notes","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"Contributed Notes","type":"text"}],"isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":4}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":5},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Missing anything? Corrections? "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-Sessions","text":"Related Sessions","level":2},{"type":"links","style":"list","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-720-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay-Creating-Great-Customer-Experiences","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-718-Introducing-Core-NFC","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-703-Apple-Pay-on-the-Web","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-704-Whats-New-with-Wallet-and-Apple-Pay"]},{"type":"small","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Legal Notice"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"small","inlineContent":[{"text":"All content copyright © 2012 – 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Swift, the Swift logo, Swift Playgrounds, Xcode, Ins